snippet.title: Pokemon Legends: Arceus - Official Daybreak Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Daybreak (Ver. 1.1.0), a free content update for Pokémon Legends: Arceus, is available now. The update brings massive mass outbreaks and more to the open-world RPG.

Pokémon Legends: Arceus is available now on Nintendo Switch.

#IGN #Pokemon
